</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eBHgEO eUYsjc pf-67_ pf-text-1"><strong>Tailored courses</strong> - Providing first aid training specific to different environments such as industrial sites or offices, addressing the particular risks found in each.

